the other guys alone *

10:22.890 --> 10:25.358
It was virtually sold out.

10:25.358 --> 10:30.063
He edited this magazine for
himself, and he was betting

10:30.063 --> 10:33.200
that other young men
were interested

10:33.200 --> 10:35.803
in the same things he
was interested in,

10:35.803 --> 10:38.271
and he won that bet.

10:38.271 --> 10:40.073
* You're gonna be lonely *

10:40.073 --> 10:41.975
