10:41.975 --> 10:44.678
It was enough for me to
pay back everyone I owed,

10:44.678 --> 10:46.880
get our furniture back,

10:46.880 --> 10:51.852
and still have enough left over
to replace my 12-year-old Chevy

10:51.852 --> 10:54.688
with a brand-new
Studebaker sports car.

10:54.688 --> 10:55.989
**

10:55.989 --> 10:58.859
"May I congratulate you
on your initial issue

10:58.859 --> 11:00.894
of Playboy magazine."

11:00.894 --> 11:04.264
And it wasn't long before
fan mail started pouring in.

11:04.264 --> 11:07.400
* Don't you know
you gotta be strong? *

11:07.400 --> 11:09.269
* Leave all
the other guys alone *

11:09.269 --> 11:14.407
Readers in Oklahoma,
Colorado, and Illinois

11:14.407 --> 11:18.645
were raving about Marilyn
and the magazine.

11:18.645 --> 11:20.513
* Whoa *

11:20.513 --> 11:23.316
Even the press
gave us positive reviews.

11:23.316 --> 11:27.120
The magazine started from
nothing and was a success

11:27.120 --> 11:28.521
from its very first issue.

11:28.521 --> 11:32.860
It was as if it was
a moment and an event

11:32.860 --> 11:34.561
that was waiting to happen.

11:34.561 --> 11:37.097
**

