- Just back to back.
- Good.

11:42.202 --> 11:44.604
Yeah, with a little
explanation and, uh.

11:44.604 --> 11:48.341
We were so surprised
by the magazine's success

11:48.341 --> 11:51.378
that we hadn't even thought
about a second issue,

11:51.378 --> 11:54.782
and now we had only a week
to put one together.

12:02.689 --> 12:05.993
To make our lives easier,
we stuck to what made

12:05.993 --> 12:08.161
the magazine work
the first time,

12:08.161 --> 12:15.468
adding more party jokes,
comics, and literature,

12:15.468 --> 12:19.907
but this time, we were
missing one key component.

12:19.907 --> 12:22.175
**

12:25.578 --> 12:28.916
No. There's nothing
good here.

12:28.916 --> 12:30.884
Well, this is all
